11-0.query:
SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS from_company, MIN(t.title) AS non_polish_sequel_movie FROM cat_company_name_4 AS cn,
 cat_company_type_4 AS ct,
 cat_keyword_4 AS k,
 cat_movie_companies_4 AS mc,
 cat_movie_keyword_4 AS mk,
 cat_title_4 AS t
WHERE t.id = mk.movie_id
 AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
 AND t.id = mc.movie_id
 AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
 AND mc.company_id = cn.id
 AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
AND cn.country_code != '@param0'
AND (cn.name LIKE '@param1' OR cn.name LIKE '@param2')
AND ct.kind = '@param3'
AND k.keyword = '@param4'
AND mc.note IS NULL
AND t.production_year BETWEEN @param5 AND @param6;
